  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\n77\n9\n\nThe second coming does not begin the Kingdom; it discloses that it exists + has existed secretly for some time, the \"2nd signal.\" Then 2-74 did not just disclose the struggle for the establishing of the Kingdom but the existence of the Kingdom - secretly. It is here + I was in it + I was conscious of the rule -the will- of God, it is a divine kingdom, as predicted by Joachim of Fiore. The two disclosures (1 + 2 supra) show that the Kingdom exists -secretly- + God rules it; it is tr",
